sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant P as Postman<br/>(External System)
    participant T as Salesforce<br/>Token Endpoint
    participant A as Salesforce<br/>REST API

    Note over P,T: STEP 1 — Ask for a key (access token)
    P->>T: POST /services/oauth2/token<br/>grant_type=client_credentials<br/>client_id + client_secret
    T->>T: Check Consumer Key & Secret<br/>Look up the "Run As" user
    T-->>P: 200 OK — access_token (Bearer)<br/>+ instance_url

    Note over P,A: STEP 2 — Use the key to open the door
    P->>A: GET /services/data/vXX.0/query?q=SELECT...<br/>Header: Authorization: Bearer &lt;access_token&gt;
    A->>A: Enforce Run As user's<br/>profile + permission sets
    A-->>P: 200 OK — JSON records

    Note over P,A: Token expired? Just repeat STEP 1 —<br/>this flow has NO refresh token
